Nayo Wallace https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nayo_Wallace 0 - Nayo Wallace, also credited as Nayo K. Wallace, is an American actress. She is perhaps best known for her roles on Speed Racer as Minx, scientist and girlfriend to Racer X and on the Hub Network's Care Bears: Welcome to Care-a-Lot as the voice of Harmony Bear from its premiere on June 2, 2012 until December 8, 2012. She also portrayed the character of Sarabi in The Lion King on Broadway. -_Nayo_Wallace , also_credited as Nayo_K._Wallace , is an_American_actress .
